<br>
She sat down on the seat she was led to. Only then did she look up and glance around at those who had already begun to gather. Everything seemed rather quiet to her,except her stomach that suddenly growled. Looks around embarressed for a short moment,then settling down,trying to get as comfortable at possible in the seat which was in the middle of the room. She rests a hand on her stomach,the other resting in her lap. <br>
